🚀 Fullstack Frontend–Backend Integration (React + Express)
📌 Overview

This project demonstrates how to connect a React frontend with a Node.js + Express backend using modern fullstack practices.

It covers:

API communication between frontend and backend
Handling CORS (Cross-Origin Resource Sharing)
Using Proxy configuration for seamless development
Rendering dynamic data in React
